Module com.example.project3fx
Package com.example.project3fx

Class Profile

java.lang.Object
com.example.project3fx.Profile
All Implemented Interfaces:
Comparable<Profile>
public class Profile extends Object implements Comparable<Profile>
This is a profile class sets and create student's profile This class has a persons first name , last name, and date of birth The profile class implements the comparable interface to allow cimparisions between profiles Variables: lname = the last name of the person fname = the first name of the person dob = the date of birth of the person
Author:
harsh_patel and giancarlo_Andretta
